'''Jesse Jensen''' played [[Saesee Tiin/Legends|Saesee Tiin]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II Attack of the Clones'']]. He is the brother of [[Zachariah Jensen]] who played [[Kit Fisto/Legends|Kit Fisto]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']]. Since working on Star Wars he has gone on to become a Production Designer for the reality TV series 'Survivor'.

